urls.description: Kangaroos, koalas, and the venomous platypus take on peculiarly acrobatic personas in a new series of oil paintings by Bruno Pontiroli (previously). In Expression Corporelle, the French artist renders a cast of gymnast-emulating animals native to Australia, each with unusually strong appendages and
urls.title: Bizarrely Flexible Wildlife Twist into Acrobatic Poses in Bruno Pontiroli's Perspective-Bending Paintings
